OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,FNHS Borders boss says they cannot
OL,7,Fcommit to when waiting lists will
OL,8,Fimprove, explaining there will be no
OL,9,Fquick fix to their projected #45m
OL,10,Fdeficit.
OL,12,FKaren Hamilton, Chair of NHS Borders,
OL,13,Ftasked with the job to reduce their
OL,14,Fexpected deficit, says a target for
OL,15,Fimproved services will take years, not
OL,16,Fmonths.
