OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,FThe board has said closures, a
OL,7,Frecruitment freeze and reductions in
OL,8,Fservice have all been considered as
OL,9,Fthey continue to face significant
OL,10,Ffinancial issues.
OL,12,FShe said: "I'm not going to be able to
OL,13,Fgive you an exact date of how long
OL,14,Fthat will be.
OL,16,F"It is a long-term project, it really
OL,17,Fis. I'm not talking months, I'm
OL,18,Ftalking years.
OL,20,F"I think it will be some considerable
OL,21,Ftime before we are able to do that.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
