OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,F"I think other initiatives may come
OL,7,Finto play around the structure and
OL,8,Fdevelopment of health services in
OL,9,FScotland.
OL,11,F"There are other things that need to
OL,12,Fhappen beyond what we can do in the
OL,13,FBorders.
OL,15,F"I would love to be able to say to you
OL,16,Fthat we can fix it in a couple of
OL,17,Fyears, but I know that we won't.
