OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,F"The level of the deficit we have now
OL,7,Fis too big to be able to say that.
OL,8,FThat doesn't mean to say that we're
OL,9,Fconstantly working towards it.
OL,11,F"The issues around waiting times and
OL,12,Fstaffing is equally important to
OL,13,Fmanaging the waiting times. I think
OL,14,Fthat's the bit that means more really
OL,15,Fand truly to the public in the
OL,16,FBorders," she added.
OL,18,FMembers of the public had the
OL,19,Fopportunity to hold the future
OL,20,Fdirection of NHS Borders to account on
OL,21,F22 August 2024.
