OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,FThe NHS Borders Annual Review comes as
OL,7,Fthe health board announced plans to
OL,8,Fcut its budget by more than 10%. The
OL,9,Ffinancial deficit is projected to
OL,10,Freach #45m by March 2025.
OL,12,FAddressing whether the Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment will have to step in to
OL,14,Fhelp, Ms Hamilton said: "We have no
OL,15,Findication at the moment from the
OL,16,FScottish Government on how they might
OL,17,Faddress that.
OL,19,F"We have been tasked to continue to
OL,20,Fwork towards the savings target which
OL,21,Fis what we will do.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
