OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,F"The deficit is significant. Nobody
OL,7,Fthinks that it will be solved
OL,8,Fovernight but we constantly work
OL,9,Ftowards it.
OL,11,F"I can say that this year we've
OL,12,Fachieved more savings than we've done
OL,13,Fin any of the previous years at this
OL,14,Fpoint, essentially at the end of the
OL,15,Ffirst quarter."
OL,17,FMs Hamilton believes that regardless
OL,18,Fof the money difficulties for health
OL,19,Fservices, staff shortages are an issue
OL,20,Fnot just in the Scottish Borders but
OL,21,Facross the country.
