OL,3,CNHS Borders boss warns it will take
OL,4,Cyears to fix projected #45m deficit
OL,6,FShe said: "Workforce is always going
OL,7,Fto be a challenge and we wouldn't deny
OL,8,Fthat.
OL,10,F"We can only work with what we've got.
OL,11,FEven if we had an unlimited amount of
OL,12,Fmoney, if we can't recruit the staff
OL,13,Fthen that money is of no use.
OL,15,F"There other areas around recruitment
OL,16,Fof nurses, training, access to college
OL,17,Fplaces, which also need to be
OL,18,Faddressed beyond the health needs of
OL,19,Fpeople in the Borders."
